{
  "id": "6a07e4ca9d8378851a89c14e",
  "title": "造傲慢",
  "created": 1778902219,
  "updated": 1778902241,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca9d8378851a89c14e",
      "text": "造傲慢",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902223
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8722",
      "text": "from [2026/05/15]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902219
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4db00000000002c872e",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902236,
      "updated": 1778902236
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8723",
      "text": " 世界観:",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8724",
      "text": " \t造傲慢（Zogoman）という概念をつくった",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8725",
      "text": " \t\t造語家かつ傲慢な人物を指す言葉",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8726",
      "text": " \t\t おもしろい[zatsma.icon][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8727",
      "text": " \t\t今のところ[sta.icon]と[hiro.icon]さんかな？",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8728",
      "text": " \tこの名前、実は「●o●o man」の型であり、これを俺はダブルオーパターンと名付けている",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c8729",
      "text": " \t\t名前付け（ネーミング）のパターンを整理した「ネーミング・パターン」があって、その一つ",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c872a",
      "text": " \t\tこれに当てはまる例は、[礼儀2.0]を出した[GOROman]さん",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c872b",
      "text": " \t3つ出てきたね:",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c872c",
      "text": " \t\t造傲慢、ダブルオーパターン、ネーミング・パターン",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902241
    },
    {
      "id": "6a07e4ca00000000002c872d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1778902219,
      "updated": 1778902219
    }
  ]
}